snippet.title: Smugglers Pre-Alpha Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Smugglers of Cygnus Pre-Alpha Trailer with Gameplay
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1298770/Smugglers_of_Cygnus/
Or on Itch: https://longplaygames.itch.io/smugglers-of-cygnus

Demo coming Feb 2022 to Itch and Steam
Space Trading/Exploration/Space Sim Game
Trailer voiced by Michael Schwalbe

Check out the forum: https://forum.longplay.games/  for more info, you can also hit us up on twitter: @Longplay_Games, or join us on Matrix: https://t.co/pZHaVFsNDr
